\DOC register_trace.doc

\TYPE {register_trace.doc : string -> int ref -> unit}

\SYNOPSIS
Registers a new tracing variable.

\KEYWORDS
Tracing.

\DESCRIBE
A call to {register_trace n r} registers the integer reference
variable {r} as a tracing variable associated with name {n}.  Its
value at the time of registration is considered its default value,
which will be restored by a call to {reset_trace n} or {reset_traces}.

\FAILURE
Fails if there is already a tracing variable registered under the
name given.

\SEEALSO
current_trace, reset_trace, reset_traces, trace, traces.

\ENDDOC